text: Nancy Young Wright was a member of the Arizona House of Representatives from 2009 through 2011. She was elected to the House in November 2008. She ran for re-election in 2010, but was defeated. ==References== Category:Arizona Democrats Category:Members of the Arizona House of Representatives Category:Women state legislators in Arizona Category:21st-century American politicians Category:21st-century American women politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
